\begin_layout Subsection*

\lang english
1.
 Purpose
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

\lang english
This policy establishes the internal audit program,
 self-assessment procedures,
 and control testing methodology that the Information Operations Department uses to evaluate the implementation,
 operating effectiveness,
 and continued adequacy of controls,
 processes,
 and obligations defined throughout the ECIO Policy Manual.
\end_layout

